      <p class="muted">Last updated: 2026</p>
      <p>Templates are provided free for personal and internal business use. You may not resell, redistribute, or claim our templates as your own. All content and designs remain the property of Checklist.</p>
      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <ul><li>Use templates for your own personal or business needs</li><li>Do not resell or repackage them</li></ul>
      <p><em>Note: Replace this placeholder text with your finalized terms before launch.</em></p>
    </div></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
